which will consume most of the network bandwidth as
a side effect.


Solution : See http://www.microsoft.com/technet/security/bulletin/ms00-036.asp
Risk factor : Medium";


 desc["francais"] = "
Le hotfix pour les vulnérabilités 'ResetBrowser Frame' et
